{"tid":284814,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"疑似生腫瘤 求介紹醫生 （希望唔係）","createTime":"2017-06-15T08:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T02:37:48.000Z","uid":38623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbfa1e78998dc4f805f461717f0d67764318dbdc","tid":284814,"uid":38623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:56:29.000Z","msg":"一個月前 我右邊腋下有直徑2cm突起左 <br />\n今日睇左兩個醫生 皮膚科西醫話唔痛唔駛理就趕左我走<br />\n另一個就中醫 佢話佢唔識睇 呢d要睇西醫 不過唔似生瘡 因為紅腫熱痛無樣中 所以有機會係腫瘤 都可能係其他原因<br />\n想請問下有冇巴絲識醫生睇呢方面/知道呢啲情況應該點做 係唔係要驗清楚同埋邊度驗好？ 聽過唔少 好求其 一開始話無野 去到後期先話有事<br />\n我之前都有同一位置類似既腫 不過幾日會好返 今次咁耐都未好 所以覺得有d擔心<br />\n跪求好醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb87a9f00f3616803f5d71f4f5dea0c7d9e4e56b","tid":284814,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:58:05.000Z","msg":"淋巴癌？"},{"pid":"386d80167644a09c32eea0b73fa99cf9b0dea2a6","tid":284814,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:01:44.000Z","msg":"係咪硬硬地 個款有啲似暗瘡<br />\n不過想擠佢又擠唔到？"},{"pid":"c1bb5bbff8b0c8b7109d3ed23117cc9a9db5cf36","tid":284814,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:01:49.000Z","msg":"照mri/ct 啦屌"},{"pid":"68227e6b6d32549d59a748245a1b6cab71cc7768","tid":284814,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:04:12.000Z","msg":"試過<br />\n後來係毛孔閉塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ed33a7e7cae00528342c24239a0570913cad79","tid":284814,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過<br />\n後來係毛孔閉塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果下勁失落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a260c4c1729b1667091fcfdad25665d7b77951","tid":284814,"uid":38623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit