msg":"<blockquote>再睇多次醫生啦<br />\n如果唔係細菌感染，就係淋巴核脹大<br />\n發炎多<br />\n但亦可以係生野<br />\n要抽組織檢查</blockquote><br />\n開呢個post主要想睇下有冇人知邊個醫生識check呢方面既野 可以介紹個醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想睇多次 只係睇人地介紹既兩個 一個無理 一個唔知 所以想搵多個醫生睇"},{"pid":"cae62863dcdcd6d2e0cb3db37949a1e990a3a54d","tid":284814,"uid":51697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:41:36.000Z","msg":"發炎啫 以為你係我朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過佢唔上連發"},{"pid":"9c298b9388eb364e02583a7cd5e72bccc1e9b298","tid":284814,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>再睇多次醫生啦<br />\n如果唔係細菌感染，就係淋巴核脹大<br />\n發炎多<br />\n但亦可以係生野<br />\n要抽組織檢查</blockquote><br />\n開呢個post主要想睇下有冇人知邊個醫生識check呢方面既野 可以介紹個醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想睇多次 只係睇人地介紹既兩個 一個無理 一個唔知 所以想搵多個醫生睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基本上個個醫生都識check"},{"pid":"7fdbe13bc45885aa5e6435cb9f29a7d6d4340aa3","tid":284814,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a62ac7c74c694d05e666457eaf9676161ce833a5","tid":284814,"uid":68802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌以為咩大事 <br />\n<br />\n洗撚介紹咩  普通集團式咩基建康建果D檢查都知係咪啦<br />\n<br />\n宜家D 90後真係唔用腦</blockquote><br />\n其實我係想搵個好醫生 睇下咩事先 因為我同識既人都無睇過皮膚科 人地介紹既連睇都唔睇<br />\n所以上面先話求個好醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>絕大部分係淋巴脹大<br />\n如果無大到唔駛理<br />\n通常用超聲波照<br />\n但要confirm要做biopsy <br />\n但公家嘅情況你依d唔急良性仲要無影響應該要排3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出私家做biopsy應該要幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果係腫瘤會大得好快<br />\n放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5163c0b8e17d26253a486c5fa8ca0e0381d8e9","tid":284814,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:46:06.000Z","msg":"通常係淋巴結腫大，未必係淋巴癌。<br />\n耳背/兩頷/耳珠/腋下有時都會發現有。<br />\n唔痛嘅話多數兩~三個禮拜會退，有時痛都冇事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：個人經驗"},{"pid":"60d3624a64ca710199963b33898dfe6f6144f8e7","tid":284814,"uid":118810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"借post問 <br />\n我係絲 最近發現個胸既側邊有粒5蚊銀大細既硬塊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇過 通常咁後生唔會係cancer <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (宜家20都未到<br />\n好撚驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔想比屋企人知 費事佢地擔心<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪真係唔痛 冇其他症狀 就可以唔理粒野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d89463b2396583955524d8e9cb1b242bfa7bc1c","tid":284814,"uid":15945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借post問 <br />\n我係絲 最近發現個胸既側邊有粒5蚊銀大細既硬塊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇過 通常咁後生唔會係cancer <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (宜家20都未到<br />\n好撚驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔想比屋企人知 費事佢地擔心<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪真係唔痛 冇其他症狀 就可以唔理粒野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncancer特點<br />\n初期無痛 左右推佢唔係好推得郁 粒野摸落係不規則形狀"},{"pid":"47c5d2ea169fd41220273cd4f1f481fa5b4facc1","tid":284814,"uid":68802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借post問 <br />\n我係絲 最近發現個胸既側邊有粒5蚊銀大細既硬塊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.